name: **** Asian Hornet Before Getting Into Freezing Season ****
description: Description:  Original photograph shot by the photographer "Nvar Kawan" from Kurdistan Region, Iraq.  The Asian giant hornet (Vespa mandarinia), including the color form referred to as the Japanese giant hornet, is the world's largest hornet.  I Caught this hornet just before getting into the freezing season, so I prepared a small background paper and grabbed it and this is what the camera accomplished. No pixel manipulation was done on this photograph.
